          "rangeEnd": 33435,
          "markText": "“蒋介石是咱们的运输大队长。”毛泽东曾经开玩笑说，他说的是事实。",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1719470656,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-06-27 14:44:16",
